                <div class = "finalstatement">
                    <div class = "final-subtitle"> final statement:</div>
                    Although gender inequality reached its apex in the 1900s, and has improved over the years, females in STEM are still not receiving as many opportunities as males. Unless the current population strives to truly and genuinely resolve this issue, it will negatively impact the world’s future generations to come. 
